data.title: Ellie Darcey-Alden - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Ellie Darcey-Alden: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

English actress who played the role of Lily Evans in the film Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows - Part 2 and the role of Francesca "Franny" Latimer in the Doctor Who series Christmas special The Snowmen.

Before Fame

She started acting in 2007 in small British stage and television roles that included a debut in a production of Aladdin.

Trivia

She also played a role in the musical production Chitty Chitty Bang Bang for the New Theatre Oxford.

Family Life

She was born to parents Phil and Sarah Alden. She has a younger brother Joseph who's also an actor and two older half siblings named Rebecca and James.
